---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { YouTube } from 'astro-embed';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Mike — Beyond Paralysis">
	<main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
		<div class="card-glow rounded-2xl p-10 sm:p-14">
			<div class="text-center mb-8">
				<img src="/sc_icon.png" alt="" class="h-16 w-auto mx-auto mb-6 opacity-60" />
				<h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About Mike</h1>
			</div>

			<p class="text-slate-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
				After 24 years of living with a C4-5 complete spinal cord injury (2023), I took the risk of getting the 'latest' & [as far as I'm aware] only commercially available treatment that has the possibility of 'restoring' some of my long lost function. I flew from the UK to Bangkok for epidural stimulation treatment, injection of stem cells & intensive rehabilitation. It was one hell of a journey! Check out the video for the full story…
			</p>

			<div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-6">
				<YouTube id="gPr4XiVQHf4" />
			</div>

			<div class="text-center">
				<a href="/" class="inline-block mt-4 text-sm text-clinical-accent hover:underline no-underline">
					&larr; Back to Home
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</BaseLayout>
